{
  "texts": [
    "There are elements in the AM dataset that rely on several parents.",
    "Since TANL's joint entity and relation extraction operation simply adds annotations to the input text without repeating or deleting anything, the output format is unable to represent such structures in text.",
    "Two representations are used to handle components with many parents: serial representation and repeating representation3. 1 illustrates.",
    "Additionally, we found that compared to the other two datasets, CDCP has a higher number of components that depend on several other components.",
    "In earlier research, TANL carried out thorough finetuning-a procedure that involves updating every parameter-on the T5-Base."
  ]
}